,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg></a><h1 id=3D"multi-object-tracking-with-ultr=
alytics-yolo">Multi-Object Tracking with Ultralytics YOLO</h1><p><img alt=
=3D"YOLO multi-object tracking with trajectory paths" src=3D"https://cdn.js=
delivr.net/gh/ultralytics/assets@main/docs/multi-object-tracking-examples.a=
vif" width=3D"1024"></p><p>Object tracking in the realm of video analytics =
is a critical task that not only identifies the location and class of objec=
ts within the frame but also maintains a unique ID for each detected object=
 as the video progresses. The applications are limitless=E2=80=94ranging fr=
om surveillance and security to real-time sports analytics.</p><h2 id=3D"wh=
y-choose-ultralytics-yolo-for-object-tracking">Why Choose Ultralytics YOLO =
for Object Tracking?</h2><p>The output from Ultralytics trackers is consist=
ent with standard <a href=3D"https://www.ultralytics.com/glossary/object-de=
tection">object detection</a> but has the added value of object IDs. This m=
akes it easy to track objects in video streams and perform subsequent analy=
tics. Here's why you should consider using Ultralytics YOLO for your object=
 tracking needs:</p><ul><li><strong>Efficiency:</strong> Process video stre=
ams in real-time without compromising <a href=3D"https://www.ultralytics.co=
m/glossary/accuracy">accuracy</a>.</li><li><strong>Flexibility:</strong> Su=
pports multiple tracking algorithms and configurations.</li><li><strong>Eas=
e of Use:</strong> Simple Python API and CLI options for quick integration =
and deployment.</li><li><strong>Customizability:</strong> Easy to use with =
custom-trained YOLO models, allowing integration into domain-specific appli=
cations.</li></ul><p align=3D"center"><br><iframe allow=3D"accelerometer; a=
utoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; w=
